{
  "name": "pi-wechat-bridge",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "description": "在微信中管理多个 Pi Agent 会话，支持 #work / #chat / #english 一键切换，图片缓存合并，多会话并发处理。One WeChat, multiple AI coding sessions.",
  "type": "module",
  "main": "dist/index.js",
  "bin": {
